article_title: Insurance Covers Four In Five Visits To CVS And Walgreen Clinics

article_metadata.description: Insurance coverage for retail health clinics, once a cash-only proposition, now accounts for more than four in five visits reimbursed at such centers run by CVS Health (CVS) and Walgreens Boots Alliance (WBA). Commercial coverage and reimbursement from the Medicare health insurance program for the elderly and Medicaid programs for low income [...]
